{"tid":215603,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"女朋友今日突然話唔想再成日傾電話","createTime":"2017-04-24T13:41:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-20T03:12:35.000Z","uid":28052,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"55bb146adfa1ddb80922ba37aac88fd9a06120d4","tid":215603,"uid":28052,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T13:41:28.000Z","msg":"其實日日傾已經傾左半年 基本上大家除咗瞓緊覺返緊學出緊街之外都會傾住電話<br />\n但係佢今日突然之間話唔想再咁樣 話想有啲私人空間<br />\n唔知點解我總係凝住佢係有其他原因<br />\n同埋覺得可能係long d關係<br />\n家下連電話都唔傾好冇安全感<br />\n唉 我可以點 好想喊<br />\n我為佢付出所有 到頭來原來只係自己難受"},{"pid":"51ff15d3585956c8c67e18eb63816c5ea430403a","tid":215603,"uid":47328,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T13:43:01.000Z","msg":"等錢駛做ptgf冇咁多時間傾電話"},{"pid":"a8280fa0e748119eae59952ce16c093ef7bc37ef","tid":215603,"uid":64131,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T13:43:53.000Z","msg":"忍左你好耐"},{"pid":"e6cf6b6d00c5eb7212cba85c505e4e04d76b4546","tid":215603,"uid":102661,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T13:46:24.000Z","msg":"長時間傾真係好累，咩都做唔到，一方面要聽對方講乜，一方面做自己野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7c9573e8d0e85b407f838d850c15be03e4e5887","tid":215603,"uid":68084,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T13:46:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\">無野既 佢需要私人空間</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f58ffeee3712a931333a609a563eb292903f73ac","tid":215603,"uid":37204,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T13:46:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>長時間傾真係好累，咩都做唔到，一方面要聽對方講乜，一方面做自己野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nagger..."},{"pid":"b2e8682f9e41d94473860a4fe896441b0179e100","tid":215603,"uid":64131,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T13:53:01.000Z","msg":"你條女對腳好好奶呀"},{"pid":"d5218101afe687d45a6c479888efc2405570eadc","tid":215603,"uid":6359