朋友咁 又係long d<br />\n最後分左手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正確來講同佢係long long d<br />\n因為佢唔係香港人就算我返到香港都冇得成日見到佢 所以其實我都覺得自己自己帶帽機會都幾大 因為佢真係好多人追 原本仲plan好哂機票都買埋諗住暑假去搵佢 唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1609de8db5dc5c2af98a14337e3db6f4e1b7212d","tid":215603,"uid":49258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T13:59:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\">帽事</span>"},{"pid":"2f405bea8fb3fa9ed301e32c52a4710034e6ce98","tid":215603,"uid":30966,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T14:00:07.000Z","msg":"私人空間 姐係佢同第二條仔嘅私人空間"},{"pid":"72deee1a33e6c9c2e6430b55df836a2b1b25d50d","tid":215603,"uid":28052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T14:01:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Move on 啦，9成淡左想搵過個<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唉 明明尋日仲傾緊電話 今日就咁樣<br />\n當初明明講好咗話要每日都傾電話每日都要搵大家<br />\n而家好似佢只係變咗單純交代俾我知去邊食咗咩咁</blockquote><br />\n佢一路淡緊無同你講咋，到今日講得已經淡左，long d 真係好難keep <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同埋我一直都覺得佢無話好鍾意我 所以我經常都會懷疑佢會唔會同幾多男仔有嘢 因為佢本身都好多人追"},{"pid":"92850b5e8069dd1c96f6a1067816491f5aa547ca","tid":215603,"uid":15921,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T14:01:45.000Z","msg":"大佬，無時無刻講電話好難頂架，有咁多野講咩"},{"pid":"274231add88368ff573572cca542ebc2cb602c04","tid":215603,"uid":28052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T14:01:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>私人空間 姐係佢同第二條仔嘅私人空間</blockquote><br />\n唉 喊出黎<br />\n他朝君體也相同"},{"pid":"3ed7faedaf891063cba7b415886ff88eabe9a7df","tid":215603,"uid":28052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T14:02:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大佬，無時無刻講電話好難頂架，有咁多野講咩</blockquote><br />\n有時會deadair 但係大部份時間都會講野<br />\n因為始終唔同國籍同埋文化唔同所以都幾多野講"},{"pid":"f8606740296b890c94b33a095a4ed39beaa4d7f0","tid":215603,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T14:04:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Move on 啦，9成淡左想搵過個<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唉 明明尋日仲傾緊電話 今日就咁樣<br />\n當初明明講好咗話要每日都傾電話每日都要搵大家<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">而家好似佢只係變咗單純交代俾我知去邊食咗咩咁</span></blockquote><br />\n即係同你冇話題呀<br />\n一係你就改變下<br />\n一係你就俾啲空間人啦"},{"pid":"e510d5919bcbbe0530ed8b4762f1eeae35b70721","tid":215603,"uid":98101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T14:06:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我試過好似你女朋友咁 又係long d<br />\n最後分左手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正確來講同佢係long long d<br />\n因為佢唔係香港人就算我返到香港都冇得成日見到佢 所以其實我都覺得自己自己帶帽機會都幾大 因為佢真係好多人追 原本仲plan好哂機票都買埋諗住暑假去搵佢 唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nLong long d 姐係文化唔同啦？ 但文化唔同好難搞<br />\n其次 長時間講電話係好難 邊有咁多野講 你或佢都要做自己野 <br />\n<br />\n利申過來人 ， 已散"},{"pid":"5dfa4d25cab817efabcfd3db219a09cae64919d6","tid":215603,"uid":28052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T14:08:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Move on 啦，9成淡左想搵過個<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唉 明明尋日仲傾緊電話 今日就咁樣<br />\n當初明明講好咗話要每日都傾電話每日都要搵大家<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">而家好似佢只係變咗單純交代俾我知去邊食咗咩咁</span></blockquote><br />\n即係同你冇話題呀<br />\n一係你就改變下<br />\n一係你就俾啲空間人啦</blockquote><br />\n唔知係咪因爲尋日世界大戰 我掛住睇無理佢 所以就咁 佢頭先都有講最近好似成日hold住電話無野講<br />\n但係覺得係依個原因嘅機會都幾細"},{"pid":"a979d120d688b0532ba07d5f677f2f6c4dccdbc4","tid":215603,"uid":90479,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T14:09:01.000Z","msg":"頭先你同佢傾果時聽唔驪到: 嗯..嗯...唔唔...啊..."},{"pid":"e313e023d93f386cc7046a354ab6a12858779935","tid":215603,"uid":28052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T14:09:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我試過好似你女朋友咁 又係long d<br />\n最後分左手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正確來講同佢係long long d<br />\n因為佢唔係香港人就算我返到香港都冇得成日見到佢 所以其實我都覺得自己自己帶帽機會都幾大 因為佢真係好多人追 原本仲plan好哂機票都買埋諗住暑假去搵佢 唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nLong long d 姐係文化唔同啦？ 但文化唔同好難搞<br />\n其次 長時間講電話係好難 邊有咁多野講 你或佢都要做自己野 <br />\n<br />\n利申過來人 ， 已散</blockquote><br />\n我同佢都係學生所以還好 佢就啱啱考完試我就下星期考 但係而家咁樣搞一搞我都冇乜心機溫書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f071a6e971c45a4983c83d75b893f9a841d17b62","tid":215603,"uid":28052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T14:09:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>頭先你同佢傾果時聽唔驪到: 嗯..嗯...唔唔...啊...</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7456d913969c737e3eee4beb50d1c8330e00dfc2","tid":215603,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T14:22:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>大佬，無時無刻講電話好難頂架，有咁多野講咩</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有時會deadair 但係大部份時間都會講野</span><br />\n因為始終唔同國籍同埋文化唔同所以都幾多野講</blockquote><br />\n你地主持電台／網台節目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3486a9f82484b8886c805f213e0c8813eb4eefa","tid":215603,"uid":33206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T14:26:06.000Z","msg":"佢私人空間都比我填滿了，對不起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"023f2cc048518590f87a0e6e7e5d3b53cc726300","tid":215603,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T14:30:18.000Z","msg